vulnerabilities.suggested_fix:
Restrict access to the minting function. Implement an ownership or role-based access control system (e.g., OpenZeppelin's `Ownable` or `AccessControl`).

Example fix:
```solidity
address public owner;
modifier onlyOwner() { require(msg.sender == owner, "Not owner"); _; }

// In constructor: owner = msg.sender;

function _0xae3550(address _0x4f9b02, uint256 _0x8e6f03) external onlyOwner {
    _0x0f4194[_0x4f9b02] += _0x8e6f03;
    _0x2c833f += _0x8e6f03;
}
```
